{"tid":2193292,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"樓爆！凱帆軒2座27A海景單位675萬成交","createTime":"2020-09-07T16:48:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T17:14:24.000Z","uid":24209,"like":14,"dislike":113,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"838d810a4767a0081808525fdf033f04a0d388ca","tid":2193292,"uid":24209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T16:48:50.000Z","msg":"2020/09/07<br />\n大角咀/奧運站<br />\n凱帆軒<br />\n2座27 A室<br />\n售: $675 萬<br />\n465呎<br />\n$14,516.1/呎<br />\n<br />\n樓價高企，有年輕買家為求上車，於農曆七月入市購買凶宅單位。美聯物業助理區域經理潘鎮煒表示，大角咀凱帆軒2座中層A室，實用面積465方呎，屬兩房間隔，雖然單位於2015年曾發生事故，但內櫳屬企理，吸引一對信奉基督教的年輕情侶以675萬元承接，作結婚用途，呎價1.45萬元。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，上述單位曾發生墮樓事故，撇除事故因素，同類單位的市價一般接近1,000萬元水平，現成交價較市價低約三成。資料顯示，原業主於2015年1月以532萬元購入上址，是次轉手帳面獲利143萬元，升值約27%。"},{"pid":"9c8c64d4a571e51f64f30270fb82aba36d5364b7","tid":2193292,"uid":71175,"like":203,"dislike":1,"score":202,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T17:00:59.000Z","msg":"真係跳樓價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec950fe765221efa519d6dd91e577a3575246f3e","tid":2193292,"uid":265485,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T17:10:47.000Z","msg":"有信念 唔怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c6aef6cfbc0fa86d4f10559fbb7c1199fcb6e7b","tid":2193292,"uid":180401,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T17:11:36.000Z","msg":"凶宅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55dc03882f03849ceb7ce3a455a9d163bf4ab553","tid":2193292,"uid":363060,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T17:15:08.000Z","msg":"睇嚟真係好凶"},{"pid":"163d65cf106e21f805eb4c75dec328744a722a3e","tid":2193292,"uid":74254,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T17:27:30.000Z","msg":"點做按揭？會唔會過一個月又撻？"},{"pid":"451b6f4ac75349ab0655c71a80bfc2950431